<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hill Stations</title>
  <style>
    /* Global Styles */
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: black;
      background-color: black;
    }

    nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: flex-start; /* Aligns navigation to the left */
            align-items: center;
            padding-left: 20px; /* Adds spacing from the edge */
        }

        nav ul {
            list-style: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            gap: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li {
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        nav ul li a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 15px;
           
        }

    

    .container {
      max-width: 1200px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }

    /* Header Section */
    .hero-section {
      position: relative;
      height: 400px;
      background: url('https://www.aanavandi.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ksrtc-munnar-Riyas-Paloli%E2%80%8E.jpg') center/cover no-repeat;
      color: #fff;
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end;
    }

    .hero-section h1 {
      margin: 20px;
      font-size: 3rem;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }
    
    /* Tabs Section */
    .tabs {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      background: #222;
      padding: 10px 0;
    }

    .tab {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      color: #ccc;
      transition: color 0.3s;
    }

    .tab:hover,
    .tab.active {
      color: #fff;
    }

    /* Cards Section */
    .cards {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
      gap: 20px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #222;
      border-radius: 8px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    }

    .card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 200px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .card-content {
      padding: 15px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin: 0;
      color: #fff;
    }

    .card p {
      margin: 10px 0;
      color: #aaa;
    }

    .card a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #4caf50;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-section h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
      }

      .tabs {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: center;
      }

      .tab {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li><a href="/home">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="/destination">Destinations</a></li>
            <li><a href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
  <div class="hero-section">
    <h1>Explore Hill Stations</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <!-- Tabs -->
    <div class="tabs">
      <div class="tab active">Famous Hill Stations</div>
      <div class="tab">Best Time to Visit</div>
      <div class="tab">Travel Tips</div>
      <div class="tab">Top Attractions</div>
    </div>

    <!-- Cards -->
    <div class="cards">

        <!-- Card 1 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/licensed-image?q=tbn:ANd9GcTxpqXAUt1ZeQ6XMFlUCQRQUlWJbrh6p4IBK93goWCcrDT7N6OeFGMrn8CkjG6SafHXsyzb1sGDRbLiVDk7tQghLmIGyJlnkhPJMOQgzg" alt="Mussoorie">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>Mussoorie, Uttarakhand</h3>
              <p>Known as the 'Queen of Hills', Mussoorie offers breathtaking views of the Himalayan range.</p>
              <a href="/Mussoorie">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://jollymiles.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/img_20201230_104356.jpg?w=1000" alt="McLeod Ganj">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>McLeod Ganj, Himachal Pradesh</h3>
              <p>Home to the Dalai Lama, this hill station offers a peaceful retreat and scenic landscapes.</p>
              <a href="/McLeodGanj">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://www.thegranddragonladakh.com/blog/admin/assets/img/post/image_2023-08-22-05-49-39_64e44c731bc7e.jpg" alt="Leh-Ladakh">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>Leh-Ladakh, Jammu & Kashmir</h3>
              <p>Experience the rugged beauty of the high mountains and crystal-clear lakes in the Himalayas.</p>
              <a href="/Ladakh">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://www.savaari.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/rasheda-akter-H1j7GqWsfpI-unsplash.jpg" alt="Shillong">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>Shillong, Meghalaya</h3>
              <p>Known as the 'Scotland of the East', Shillong is famous for its lush greenery and waterfalls.</p>
              <a href="Shillong">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/p/AF1QipNtBishnc1Io2IEThUYQrJFIG2ckdadz-XEBl1G=w540-h312-n-k-no" alt="Nainital">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>Nainital, Uttarakhand</h3>
              <p>Set around a beautiful lake, Nainital is known for its serene surroundings and vibrant market.</p>
              <a href="/Nainital">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 6 -->
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://experiencemyindia.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Kullu-Manali-Blog.jpg" alt="Kullu">
            <div class="card-content">
              <h3>Kullu, Himachal Pradesh</h3>
              <p>Experience the natural beauty of Kullu, known for its apple orchards and scenic valleys.</p>
              <a href="/Kullu">Explore Packages</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>